[Amit Varma]: but you guys have met me in person and have known me for many years.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:53.120
[Amit Varma]: So you know the unseen.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:56.600
[Amit Varma]: And by the way, Nitin, if I want to do a seven hour episode with you when I next come to

